title: Jacques Brel videos - mp4 (iPod) format
description:
Sixty videos, most in black and white, of Jacques Brel singing his own songs.  If you haven&#039;t seen Brel present it his work French, you&#039;re missing the real thing. This is it.

Some videos have subtitles (English, Dutch, Spanish); this is usually noted in the filename.  All are in mp4 format (iPod/iTunes).  If anyone is interested, I also have them in mpg format (Windoze Media Player, VCD, etc.), but they&#039;re a lot bigger.

Enjoy!
